	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Apparently this is the hottest new youtuber gimmick game since youtube won't stop recommending &quot;&quot;funny&quot;&quot; videos about it. <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/app/240720/Getting_Over_It_with_Bennett_Foddy/" class="postlink">&quot;Getting over it with Bennett Foddy&quot;</a> is the name of it, and it makes me wonder if our friend tepples inspired or is part of it. If I remember correctly he was toying with similar concepts for his trademark round bottom characters in which the player had to use a Bionic Commando like grapple gun to navigate the level.<br /><br />Tepples, did you have a hand in this? If not you might want to check it out to see if you can employ something like that for a future game of yours. The character design is somewhat similar to the ones you have.<br /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.foddy.net/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/thumb.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lOHHsUAyGVU">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lOHHsUAyGVU</a><!-- m -->

		

