		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I love that game. I think it's actually my favourite game of the year.<br /><br />I'd recommend not watching that speedrun video as your introduction to it, though. It shows you the whole game and a way to solve it (which will take practice, but a lot of the fun is experimenting and learning). Instead maybe a let's play with all the frustration of failing would give a much better and less spoilery introduction to what it is.<br /><br />(Seems to be tricky to find a LPer of this who isn't constantly annoyingly screaming at it, though, or I'd link one myself.)<br /><br />This one seems okay:<br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VewagdAZjFA" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VewagdAZjFA</a>

		

